%h1 Words
%p
    We have
    =@words.count
    word in database!

%table.table
    %thead
        %tr
            %th
                \#
            %th
                Value
            %th 
                Language
        %tbody
            - @words.each do |word|
                %tr
                    %td= word.id
                    %td= word.value
                    %td= word.language

                    
